<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="minimum-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,initial-scale=1,user-scalable=no,width=device-width" />
<title>触 &middot; 爱</title>
</head>

<body>
<style type="text/css">
*{ margin:0px; padding:0px;}
#loveHeart{max-width:650px;height:650px; margin:0 auto; position:relative; overflow:hidden;}
#garden{width:100%;height:100%; position:absolute; top:0px; left:0px;}
#words{font-family:"sans-serif";width:185px;font-size:20px;color:#666; text-align:left; display:block; line-height:30px; margin:185px auto 0px; display:none;}
#words strong{ font-weight:100; -webkit-transition:1s all ease-out;}
</style>
<div id="loveHeart">
	<canvas id="garden"></canvas>
    <div id="words">
        <p><strong>朱</strong>阁雅淡心照宣，</p>
        <p><strong>梦</strong>绕萦回情愫间。</p>
        <p><strong>娇</strong>美如画眉宇悬，</p>
        <p><strong>我</strong>虽有心夜难眠。</p>
        <p><strong>爱</strong>挚心诚愿无憾，</p>
        <p><strong>你</strong>眸一笑此生恋。</p>
    </div>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../js/jquery-2.1.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="js/garden_dev.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="js/index.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
